NOTICE OF DELINQUENT FINES LIEN
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN that, pursuant to the provisions of the Nevada Revised
Statutes, COTTONWOODS OWNERS ASSOCIATION claims a lien upon the real property
and buildings, improvements, or structures thereon, described in Paragraph 2 below, and states
the following:
1.
The amount of the fines, late charges, interest, costs and penalties is $2,375.93 as of
May 17, 2021, and may increase for any additional fines or penalties for future violations that
do not pose an imminent threat of causing a substantial adverse effect on the health, safety or
welfare of the residents of Cottonwoods Owners Association, in the amount of $100.00 per
week or portion thereof, per violation, from March 14, 2021, for continued violation of Article
VII, Section 7 (c) of the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions of
Cottonwoods at Hafen Ranch, (failure to trim or remove all overgrown vegetation and weeds
from the lot) as well as for any additional attorney fees and fees of the agent for the
management body incurred in connection with preparation, recording and foreclosure of this
lien and/or which may thereafter accrue.
2.
The property against which the assessment is assessed is described as follows:
Lot Six (5) in Block Five (5) of Cottonwoods at Hafen Ranch
Unit 2 Phase No. 2, as shown by map thereof recorded April 8,
1992 as File No. 306430 and amended by Certificate of
Amendment recorded June 24, 1992 as File No. 310866 and
amended by map recorded April 7, 1993 as File No. 329165, in
the office of the County Recorder of Nye County, Nevada, more
commonly known as: 5581 East Mary Lou Street, Pahrump,
Nevada 89061.
